like":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"佢唔能夠面對, 佢半世人既信仰及事業已經變成無意義既事實<br />\n<br />\n人在面臨挫折時，會經歷5個階段：否認 Denial、憤怒 Anger、討價還價 Bargaining、沮喪 Deperssion 與接受 Acceptance。<br />\n<br />\n否認&rarr;憤怒&rarr;討價還價&rarr;沮喪&rarr;接受<br />\n<br />\n否認：當事人會認為這件事不是真的，不應該發生在自己身上。<br />\n憤怒：此時負面情緒產生，會開始抱怨，甚至牽怒他人。<br />\n討價還價：有的人會跟老天祈求，希望得到幫忙或轉運；然後當義工回報上天的回應。<br />\n沮喪：當事人可能作了一些努力或改變企圖解決，但可能途勞無功，而產生無力感。<br />\n接受：當事人漸漸接受了事實的真像，開始重新回歸正常生活。"},{"pid":"bd5c3d20dfa0af75528aaa6af0cfadf0068c458c","tid":2081834,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"法治已死<br />\n又唔肯認"},{"pid":"f570be9b83aec2503ff1d2f707163556cdbcd72c","tid":2081834,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"咁over 你的dead body先"},{"pid":"0798818780f3ec8656059eb72ad136a784e6dcad","tid":2081834,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc72f98957a84d800d7ae99c5d13758a647a5d9d","tid":2081834,"uid":196839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"劉偉聰扮同情本土<br />\n實質保守過公民黨<br />\n一嚿雲都識得話一齊衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"劣師扮本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51e3cc2597456c04213de8ef8bd6f2da52ea7b2","tid":2081834,"uid":246262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"屌同埋佢呢啲乞人憎大狀格係想吸引邊類選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214a7e5fd483e345541b138c9a9ce99ae1971ebc","tid":2081834,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e51e3cc2597456c04213de8ef8bd6f2da52ea7b2","tid":2081834,"uid":246262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T15:29:05.000Z",